OL,3,CWater boss should not resign as
OL,4,Cproblem 'far wider than individual
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FThe chief executive officer of the
OL,8,Fwater company involved in a major
OL,9,Fsupply issue in Kent should not resign
OL,10,Fas issues in the industry go "far
OL,11,Fwider than individual people", a
OL,12,Fdirector has said.
OL,14,FSouth East Water (SEW) has issued a
OL,15,F"boil water notice" for 24,000 homes
OL,16,Fin and around Tunbridge Wells who have
OL,17,Fexperienced a loss of water or low
OL,18,Fpressure since November 29.
