OL,3,CWater boss should not resign as
OL,4,Cproblem 'far wider than individual
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FOn Wednesday (3 December), the company
OL,8,Fsaid the "water quality issues" which
OL,9,Fcaused the initial shutdown had
OL,10,Freturned.
OL,12,FThey decided to continue pumping water
OL,13,Fso that people could flush their
OL,14,Ftoilets and shower, but the water
OL,15,Fcannot be drunk without being boiled
OL,16,Ffirst.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@_O]
