OL,3,CWater boss should not resign as
OL,4,Cproblem 'far wider than individual
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FSEW says the taps will be back to
OL,8,Fnormal in Tunbridge Wells by Friday
OL,9,Fand the precautionary boil notice will
OL,10,Fbe lifted by the end of the week, if
OL,11,Feverything goes to plan.
OL,13,FThey say supply has returned to all
OL,14,Faffected customers, and no bacteria
OL,15,Fhad been detected in the water.
OL,17,FLiberal Democrat MP Mike Martin said
OL,18,Fthat the situation had been "a total
OL,19,Ffailure of leadership" and called for
OL,20,Fthe chief executive of SEW, Dave
OL,21,FHinton, to resign.
OL,26,@zD@]OU{D@VO]
