OL,3,CWater boss should not resign as
OL,4,Cproblem 'far wider than individual
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FDouglas Whitfield, SEW water supply
OL,8,Fdirector, said resignation demands
OL,9,F"fundamentally misunderstand the
OL,10,Fchallenges that we've been facing in
OL,11,Fthis incident as a company over the
OL,12,Flast few years, as an industry going
OL,13,Fforward, I don't think that's helpful".
OL,15,FHe said: "I would point you to the
OL,16,Findependent Water Commission that sets
OL,17,Fout the challenges the water industry
OL,18,Fare facing and the changes it needs to
OL,19,Fmake.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@fO]wD@JOU
