OL,3,CWater boss should not resign as
OL,4,Cproblem 'far wider than individual
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,F"They're far wider than individual
OL,8,Fcompany and individual people."
OL,10,FMr Whitfield apologised to customers
OL,11,Fand said the precautionary boil notice
OL,12,Fwas in place for 10 days because
OL,13,F"public health is our key priority".
OL,15,FBut he said he was unable to guarantee
OL,16,Fthe problem ensuring water quality
OL,17,Fwould be solved within the 10 days as
OL,18,Fhe was unable to provide a "definitive
OL,19,Fanswer" as to why the water was not
OL,20,Fresponding to normal treatment.
