OL,3,CWater boss should not resign as
OL,4,Cproblem 'far wider than individual
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FHe said: "For the last 24 hours, the
OL,8,Ftreatment process has actually been
OL,9,Foperating within all of the water
OL,10,Fquality parameters.
OL,12,F"Until we're confident that we've
OL,13,Fresolved the issue and that it won't
OL,14,Freoccur, we'll be working to keep that
OL,15,Fboil notice in place, until we are
OL,16,Fconfident we can take it off.
OL,18,F"I can confirm all the water we
OL,19,Fsupplied up to the point we put the
OL,20,Fboil notice on fully complied with all
OL,21,Fthe regulations."
