OL,3,CWater boss should not resign as
OL,4,Cproblem 'far wider than individual
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FMr Whitfield apologised for "overly
OL,8,Foptimistic" messages put out to
OL,9,Fcustomers since the problem started
OL,10,Fbut said this was "one of the most
OL,11,Fcomplex events that we've ever had".
OL,13,FHe added: "I can only apologise to the
OL,14,Fcustomers for the last week and the
OL,15,Fcommunications that we gave during the
OL,16,Fincident were on what we thought was
OL,17,Fgoing to happen at the time.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@KO]rD@SOUsD@cO]uD@KOU
