OL,3,CWater boss should not resign as
OL,4,Cproblem 'far wider than individual
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,F"The incident has changed from what we
OL,8,Fthought was happening at the weekend
OL,9,Fto a much longer, much more
OL,10,Fcomplicated issue that we're trying to
OL,11,Fresolve."
OL,13,FThe Consumer Council for Water (CCW),
OL,14,Fan independent body representing water
OL,15,Fconsumers across England and Wales,
OL,16,Fhas called for a thorough
OL,17,Finvestigation into the incident.
